key_handles.description: A list of all the retrieved key handles

location.description: The canonical id for the location. For example: "us-east1".

resource_type_selector.description: The resource_type_selector argument is used to add a filter query parameter that limits which key handles are retrieved by the data source: ?filter=resource_type_selector="{{resource_type_selector}}". Example values: * resource_type_selector="{SERVICE}.googleapis.com/{TYPE}". [See the documentation about using filters](https://cloud.google.com/kms/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.locations.keyHandles/list)
